Golden Age Arc to your collection for $48 (was $70). The 2016 Berserk anime is also on sale for only $41 (was $70) on Blu-ray. Some longtime Berserk fans dislike how often it doesn't follow the manga, while others enjoy it for that reason. It has some visual miscues and oddities with the animation itself, but the series still has bright spots and overall is worth watching.If you want to check out the original manga, the Deluxe Editions are the way to go. All 14 of these gorgeous hardcover compilations are available at Amazon, and many of them are discounted by $15-$20. Each book contains three volumes of Berserk. Together, the 14 hardcovers collect all of the trade paperbacks written by Miura before his death in 2021. Berserk Volume 42, the first paperback without Miura's work, was published in March and honors the series creator.Berserk Deluxe Edition Volume 1 is on sale for $28.65 (was $50) at Amazon.Berserk Manga Deluxe EditionsBerserk Deluxe Edition mangaBerserk Deluxe Vol. 1 -- $28.65 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 2 -- $31.24 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 3 -- $36.22 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 4 -- $30.78 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 5 -- $27.37 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 6 -- $32.55 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 7 -- $38.30 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 8 -- $27.76 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 9 -- $44 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 10 -- $41.45 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 11 -- $29.76 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 12 -- $44 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 13 -- $44 ($50)Berserk Deluxe Vol. 14 -- $43($50) The Criterion Collection 50% Off Movie Sale - Here Are The Best Deals Little Nightmares 3 Amazon-Exclusive Mirror Edition Is Up For Preorder Lego's First Visual History For Adults Is 60% Off In Early Prime Day Deal + Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals \u0026 Preorders Links (5) Amazon Restocks Rune Factory: Guardians Of Azuma Earth Dancer Edition All Four Discontinued Donkey Kong Lego Sets Restocked At Amazon Death Stranding 2 Collector's Edition Is In Stock Ahead Of Tomorrow's Launch Donkey K